<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一行人走过了西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这条路通往灵山，路的两边鲜花盛开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒抬头看那巨大的山，摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爬那座山可不太容易。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“你别拜托我抱你啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，师徒四人走到一个水流很急的大河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>河水拍打着尖尖的岩石，水朝四方溅起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这条河看起来很危险。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，要去灵山，就得过河。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们绝对不能安全过河的，我们还是回家吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可以。”悟空说，“看那边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空指着上流那边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一个细细的木头横跨在大河上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木头下面水流很急，木头摇摇晃晃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看了看木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别傻了，悟空。我们不能用那个木头过河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它太细了，而且看起来非常滑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，那个木头是我们去灵山的唯一方法。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得相信它是安全的。看我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到木头上跑过去，又跑了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看见了吧？”他说，“很安全。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。“你很轻，悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，如果我走上那个木头，它就会断的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我相信悟空。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得从木头上走过去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我来，师父。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把唐僧朝木头那边拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧吓得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别让我从那上面走过去！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我掉到河里会淹死的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就从河上面飞过去。”八戒提议，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以抱着师父和马过去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行。”悟空主张说，“师父得一个人完成取经历程。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们在这儿是为了保护师父，不是为了抱他过河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师父如果不亲自一步一步地走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖就不会允许师父拿到真经的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一个划着小船的老人出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮你们过河。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝河岸走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的徒弟让我从那个木头上走过去……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“船有问题。”他对老人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“船没有底！进水呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“船很安全。”老人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赶紧上船吧。佛祖等着呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧犹豫了一下，上了船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到自己没有沉下去，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在船边，悟净把马牵到了船上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟空跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船在河里走得很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，传来扑通一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看了看河水，一具尸体在朝下游飘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大叫了一声。“有人掉进水里死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空把手放在唐僧肩膀上，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是你啊，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”唐僧说，“是我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空说得对！”八戒大喊，“那的确是你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你再看看，师父。”悟净笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧更仔细地看了看尸体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那尸体穿着和自己一模一样的袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的是我。”唐僧安静地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，怎么会……？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你扔掉了人类的身体，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你是仙人了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父也和我们一样了！”八戒开心地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船很快就到了对面河岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人从船上下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走在灵山的山坡上时，唐僧惊讶得哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我感觉身体很轻！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我能跑到山上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了。”八戒说，“也许可以抱着我走呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们继续上山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>